  "body": "\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"ocph-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocph-inner\">\n<div class=\"ocph-grid\">\n<div class=\"ocph-left\">\n<div class=\"ocph-eyebrow\"><div class=\"ocph-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"ocph-ey-txt\">Software Comparisons</span></div>\n<h1 class=\"ocph-h1\">SiteFlow vs<em class=\"ocph-h1-em\">The Alternatives</em></h1>\n<p class=\"ocph-sub\">Side-by-side breakdowns of how SiteFlow compares to other construction software — written for Indian and Middle East contractors who need real answers, not marketing copy.</p>\n<div class=\"ocph-pills\">\n<div class=\"ocph-pill\"><div class=\"ocph-pill-dot\"></div><span class=\"ocph-pill-txt\">India-specific criteria</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocph-pill\"><div class=\"ocph-pill-dot\"></div><span class=\"ocph-pill-txt\">BOQ and labour coverage</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocph-pill\"><div class=\"ocph-pill-dot\"></div><span class=\"ocph-pill-txt\">Pricing in INR</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocph-btns\">\n<a class=\"ocph-btn-p\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">Book Free Demo</a>\n<a class=\"ocph-btn-o\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/SiteFlow-pricing/\">See Pricing</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocph-trust\">\n<span class=\"ocph-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n<span class=\"ocph-trust-txt\"><strong>4.8 / 5</strong>  ·  Rated by 500+ construction teams</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocph-right\">\n\n          SVG 500×500. Centre (250,250). Never breaks.\n          \n          RINGS:\n            Decorative fill:  r=120, r=148\n            Inner orbit ring: r=155  (Procore, Powerplay, NYGGS)\n            Outer orbit ring: r=212  (RDash, Buildern, NWAY)\n            Outer decorative: r=232\n          \n          BADGES (Tidio-style circles, r=34):\n            Procore   320° inner  cx=150.4  cy=131.3\n            RDash      32° outer  cx=362.3  cy= 70.2\n            Powerplay 105° inner  cx=399.7  cy=290.1\n            Buildern  148° outer  cx=362.3  cy=429.8\n            NYGGS     218° inner  cx=154.6  cy=372.1\n            NWAY      255° outer  cx= 45.2  cy=304.9\n          \n          All verified: in bounds, min gap 128px between any two centres.\n        \n<svg class=\"ocph-svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 500 500\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<defs>\n<radialgradient cx=\"50%\" cy=\"28%\" id=\"og-c\" r=\"70%\">\n<stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#f87099\"></stop>\n<stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#bf0840\"></stop>\n</radialgradient>\n<radialgradient cx=\"50%\" cy=\"50%\" id=\"og-glow\" r=\"50%\">\n<stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.13)\"></stop>\n<stop offset=\"65%\" stop-color=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.05)\"></stop>\n<stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"rgba(211,13,80,0)\"></stop>\n</radialgradient>\n<filter height=\"180%\" id=\"of-b\" width=\"180%\" x=\"-40%\" y=\"-40%\">\n<fedropshadow dx=\"0\" dy=\"4\" flood-color=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.13)\" stddeviation=\"9\"></fedropshadow>\n<fedropshadow dx=\"0\" dy=\"1\" flood-color=\"rgba(0,0,0,0.07)\" stddeviation=\"3\"></fedropshadow>\n</filter>\n<filter height=\"200%\" id=\"of-c\" width=\"200%\" x=\"-50%\" y=\"-50%\">\n<fedropshadow dx=\"0\" dy=\"14\" flood-color=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.42)\" stddeviation=\"22\"></fedropshadow>\n<fedropshadow dx=\"0\" dy=\"4\" flood-color=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.20)\" stddeviation=\"8\"></fedropshadow>\n</filter>\n</defs>\n Ambient glow \n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"url(#og-glow)\" r=\"238\"></circle>\n Rings — outermost to innermost \n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"none\" r=\"232\" stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.07)\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"none\" r=\"212\" stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.10)\" stroke-width=\"1\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"none\" r=\"155\" stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.14)\" stroke-width=\"1\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.05)\" r=\"128\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.06)\" r=\"108\"></circle>\n Dashed connector lines: centre → each badge centre \n<line stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.20)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5 4\" stroke-width=\"1\" x1=\"250\" x2=\"150.4\" y1=\"250\" y2=\"131.3\"></line>\n<line stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.16)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5 4\" stroke-width=\"1\" x1=\"250\" x2=\"362.3\" y1=\"250\" y2=\" 70.2\"></line>\n<line stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.20)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5 4\" stroke-width=\"1\" x1=\"250\" x2=\"399.7\" y1=\"250\" y2=\"290.1\"></line>\n<line stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.16)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5 4\" stroke-width=\"1\" x1=\"250\" x2=\"362.3\" y1=\"250\" y2=\"429.8\"></line>\n<line stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.20)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5 4\" stroke-width=\"1\" x1=\"250\" x2=\"154.6\" y1=\"250\" y2=\"372.1\"></line>\n<line stroke=\"rgba(211,13,80,0.16)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5 4\" stroke-width=\"1\" x1=\"250\" x2=\" 45.2\" y1=\"250\" y2=\"304.9\"></line>\n ══ CENTRE CIRCLE (r=108) ══ \n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"url(#og-c)\" filter=\"url(#of-c)\" r=\"108\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"250\" fill=\"none\" r=\"108\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.20)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></circle>\n Logo mark \n<circle cx=\"250\" cy=\"210\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.22)\" r=\"20\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"></circle>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"250\" y=\"210\">O</text>\n Brand \n<text fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"800\" letter-spacing=\"-0.4\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"250\" y=\"240\">SiteFlow</text>\n Divider \n<line stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.22)\" stroke-width=\"0.8\" x1=\"210\" x2=\"290\" y1=\"249\" y2=\"249\"></line>\n Score \n<text fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"28\" font-weight=\"800\" letter-spacing=\"-1.2\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"248\" y=\"274\">9.2</text>\n<text fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.52)\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"600\" text-anchor=\"start\" x=\"273\" y=\"267\">/10</text>\n Label \n<text fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.52)\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"7.5\" font-weight=\"700\" letter-spacing=\"0.8\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"250\" y=\"288\">EXECUTION SCORE</text>\n Pill \n<rect fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.16)\" height=\"17\" rx=\"8.5\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.26)\" stroke-width=\"0.8\" width=\"108\" x=\"196\" y=\"297\"></rect>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.80)\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"7\" font-weight=\"700\" letter-spacing=\"0.2\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"250\" y=\"308.5\">500+ teams trust SiteFlow</text>\n\n            ══ COMPETITOR BADGES — Tidio-style circles ══\n            Each: white circle r=34, drop shadow\n                  brand colour circle r=18 at centre (icon area)\n                  letter centred in icon circle\n                  name text at cy+46 (just below circle)\n                  why text at cy+58\n            \n            All text is centred on badge cx.\n            Max text width ~68px (34px each side of cx).\n            All verified within viewBox 0-500.\n          \n Procore — cx=150.4, cy=131.3, inner ring 320° \n<circle cx=\"150.4\" cy=\"131.3\" fill=\"white\" filter=\"url(#of-b)\" r=\"34\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"150.4\" cy=\"131.3\" fill=\"#dc2626\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"150.4\" y=\"131.3\">P</text>\n<text fill=\"#0f0a1e\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"150.4\" y=\"177\">Procore</text>\n<text fill=\"#9ca3af\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"9.5\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"150.4\" y=\"191\">USD pricing</text>\n RDash — cx=362.3, cy=70.2, outer ring 32° \n<circle cx=\"362.3\" cy=\"70.2\" fill=\"white\" filter=\"url(#of-b)\" r=\"34\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"362.3\" cy=\"70.2\" fill=\"#1d4ed8\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"362.3\" y=\"70.2\">R</text>\n<text fill=\"#0f0a1e\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"362.3\" y=\"116\">RDash</text>\n<text fill=\"#9ca3af\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"9.5\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"362.3\" y=\"130\">Reports only</text>\n Powerplay — cx=399.7, cy=290.1, inner ring 105° \n<circle cx=\"399.7\" cy=\"290.1\" fill=\"white\" filter=\"url(#of-b)\" r=\"34\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"399.7\" cy=\"290.1\" fill=\"#d97706\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"399.7\" y=\"290.1\">P</text>\n<text fill=\"#0f0a1e\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"399.7\" y=\"336\">Powerplay</text>\n<text fill=\"#9ca3af\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"9.5\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"399.7\" y=\"350\">Site app only</text>\n Buildern — cx=362.3, cy=429.8, outer ring 148° \n<circle cx=\"362.3\" cy=\"429.8\" fill=\"white\" filter=\"url(#of-b)\" r=\"34\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"362.3\" cy=\"429.8\" fill=\"#7c3aed\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"362.3\" y=\"429.8\">B</text>\n<text fill=\"#0f0a1e\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"362.3\" y=\"476\">Buildern</text>\n<text fill=\"#9ca3af\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"9.5\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"362.3\" y=\"490\">US market</text>\n NYGGS — cx=154.6, cy=372.1, inner ring 218° \n<circle cx=\"154.6\" cy=\"372.1\" fill=\"white\" filter=\"url(#of-b)\" r=\"34\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"154.6\" cy=\"372.1\" fill=\"#059669\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"154.6\" y=\"372.1\">N</text>\n<text fill=\"#0f0a1e\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"154.6\" y=\"418\">NYGGS</text>\n<text fill=\"#9ca3af\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"9.5\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"154.6\" y=\"432\">HR-focused</text>\n NWAY — cx=45.2, cy=304.9, outer ring 255° \n<circle cx=\"45.2\" cy=\"304.9\" fill=\"white\" filter=\"url(#of-b)\" r=\"34\"></circle>\n<circle cx=\"45.2\" cy=\"304.9\" fill=\"#b45309\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n<text dominant-baseline=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"15\" font-weight=\"900\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"45.2\" y=\"304.9\">N</text>\n<text fill=\"#0f0a1e\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"45.2\" y=\"351\">NWAY</text>\n<text fill=\"#9ca3af\" font-family=\"-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif\" font-size=\"9.5\" text-anchor=\"middle\" x=\"45.2\" y=\"365\">Legacy ERP</text>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"ocmp-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocmp-inner\">\n<div class=\"ocmp-head\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"ocmp-ey\">All Comparisons</div>\n<h2 class=\"ocmp-h2\">SiteFlow vs <em class=\"ocmp-h2-em\">every alternative</em></h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n Grid: fully populated by JS. No hardcoded cards. \n<div class=\"ocmp-grid\" id=\"ocmp-grid\">\n<div class=\"ocmp-loading\">\n<div class=\"ocmp-loading-dots\">\n<div class=\"ocmp-loading-dot\"></div>\n<div class=\"ocmp-loading-dot\"></div>\n<div class=\"ocmp-loading-dot\"></div>\n</div>\n        Loading comparisons…\n      </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocmp-suggest\">\n<div class=\"ocmp-suggest-left\">\n<div class=\"ocmp-suggest-icon\">\n<svg fill=\"none\" height=\"24\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"24\">\n<circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-width=\"1.8\"></circle>\n<path d=\"M12 8v4M12 16h.01\" stroke=\"#d30d50\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\"></path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"ocmp-suggest-title\">Do not see your current tool?</div>\n<div class=\"ocmp-suggest-sub\">Tell us which software you want us to compare SiteFlow against — we will write it next.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<a class=\"ocmp-suggest-btn\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">\n        Suggest a comparison\n        <svg fill=\"none\" height=\"13\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"13\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"ocsp-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-wrap\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-head ocsp-anim\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-eyebrow\"><span class=\"ocsp-eyebrow-dot\"></span>What clients say</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-h2\">Teams that compared and chose SiteFlow</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-bento\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-cell ocsp-c-7 ocsp-anim ocsp-d1\" style=\"display:flex!important;flex-direction:column!important;\">\n<span class=\"ocsp-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-qmark\">“</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp-quote-lg\">We evaluated three platforms before choosing SiteFlow. The others required months of setup and a partner to implement. SiteFlow had us live in under a week — with our actual BOQ data, not a demo. That alone made the decision obvious.</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-person\" style=\"margin-top:auto!important;\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-avatar\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f43f6e,#d30d50)!important;\">RK</div>\n<div><div class=\"ocsp-name\">R. Kumar</div><div class=\"ocsp-co\">Reidius Infra, Jaipur  ·  Infrastructure Contractor</div></div>\n</div>\n<span class=\"ocsp-pill\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#a50c3c!important;border:1px solid rgba(211,13,80,0.20)!important;\">Faster Setup</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-cell ocsp-c-5 ocsp-stat-cell ocsp-anim ocsp-d2\" style=\"min-height:clamp(200px,28vw,280px)!important;\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-stat-label\">SiteFlow by numbers</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-stats-grid\">\n<div><div class=\"ocsp-stat-n\" style=\"color:#fda4b8!important;\">500+</div><div class=\"ocsp-stat-d\">construction companies using SiteFlow today</div></div>\n<div><div class=\"ocsp-stat-n\" style=\"color:#34d399!important;\">3 days</div><div class=\"ocsp-stat-d\">average time from signup to go-live</div></div>\n<div><div class=\"ocsp-stat-n\" style=\"color:#fcd34d!important;\">INR</div><div class=\"ocsp-stat-d\">project-based pricing built for India</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-cell ocsp-c-5 ocsp-anim ocsp-d3\" style=\"display:flex!important;flex-direction:column!important;\">\n<span class=\"ocsp-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp-quote-md\">We were using a global platform that charged per user and needed an implementation partner. Switching to SiteFlow cut our software costs significantly and our team was productive from day one.</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-person\" style=\"margin-top:auto!important;\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-avatar\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1d4ed8,#1e40af)!important;\">CA</div>\n<div><div class=\"ocsp-name\">Operations Manager</div><div class=\"ocsp-co\">Cyath Contracting, Dubai</div></div>\n</div>\n<span class=\"ocsp-pill\" style=\"background:#eff6ff!important;color:#1d4ed8!important;border:1px solid #bfdbfe!important;\">Cost Saving</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-cell ocsp-c-4 ocsp-tags-cell ocsp-anim ocsp-d4\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-tags-title\">What contractors found different</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-tags-cloud\">\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#a50c3c!important;border-color:rgba(211,13,80,0.20)!important;\">India pricing</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#f0fdf4!important;color:#059669!important;border-color:#bbf7d0!important;\">BOQ built-in</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#fef2f2!important;color:#dc2626!important;border-color:#fecaca!important;\">No USD per seat</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#fffbeb!important;color:#b45309!important;border-color:#fde68a!important;\">GPS attendance</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#a50c3c!important;border-color:rgba(211,13,80,0.20)!important;\">Tally sync</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#f0fdf4!important;color:#059669!important;border-color:#bbf7d0!important;\">Live in days</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#fff0f3!important;color:#a50c3c!important;border-color:rgba(211,13,80,0.20)!important;\">Subcon billing</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag\" style=\"background:#fef2f2!important;color:#dc2626!important;border-color:#fecaca!important;\">Free onboarding</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-cell ocsp-c-3 ocsp-anim ocsp-d5\" style=\"display:flex!important;flex-direction:column!important;\">\n<span class=\"ocsp-stars\" style=\"font-size:10px!important;\">★★★★★</span>\n<div class=\"ocsp-quote-sm\">After GPS attendance went live our payroll disputes stopped entirely. The site data goes straight into payroll — nothing manual in between.</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-person\" style=\"margin-top:auto!important;\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-avatar ocsp-avatar-sm\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#059669,#065f46)!important;\">SF</div>\n<div><div class=\"ocsp-name ocsp-name-sm\">Site Manager</div><div class=\"ocsp-co ocsp-co-sm\">SFC Infratech, India</div></div>\n</div>\n<span class=\"ocsp-pill\" style=\"background:#f0fdf4!important;color:#059669!important;border:1px solid #bbf7d0!important;margin-top:8px!important;\">Payroll Accuracy</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-cell ocsp-c-12 ocsp-strip-cell ocsp-anim ocsp-d6\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-person\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-avatar\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#b45309)!important;\">MM</div>\n<div><div class=\"ocsp-name\">M. Munif Al Otaibi</div><div class=\"ocsp-co\">M. Munif Al Otaibi Contracting, Saudi Arabia</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-strip-divider\"></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-strip-quote\">We looked at several software options for our Saudi Arabia projects. Most were built for Western markets and did not understand how we track labour, subcontractors, or run billing here. SiteFlow understood the Gulf market from day one and the team helped us go live within the week.</div>\n<span class=\"ocsp-stars\" style=\"flex-shrink:0!important;margin-bottom:0!important;\">★★★★★</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ocsp-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-inner\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-head ocsp-anim\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-eyebrow\"><div class=\"ocsp-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"ocsp-ey-txt\">Real Switchers</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"ocsp-h2\">Teams that <em class=\"ocsp-h2-em\">made the switch</em> to SiteFlow</h2>\n<p class=\"ocsp-sub\">Not generic testimonials — each team moved away from a specific tool and chose SiteFlow instead.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-grid\">\n Card 1: Reidius Infra — tag-p COLOR: rose \n<a class=\"ocsp-card ocsp-anim\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/case-study-reidius-infra/\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-from\"><svg class=\"ocsp-from-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg><span class=\"ocsp-from-txt\">Switched from Excel</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-company\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-logo\" style=\"background-image:url('https://siteflow.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/website-assets-square-2025-new--1024x1024.webp')!important;padding:4px!important;\"></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-company-txt\"><div class=\"ocsp-name\">Reidius Infra</div><div class=\"ocsp-role\">Infrastructure contractor, India</div></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-stars\"><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp-quote\">“We were managing everything across spreadsheets and WhatsApp groups. There was no single version of the truth. SiteFlow gave us that — every site update shows up for the office in real time.”</p>\n<div class=\"ocsp-metric\"><span class=\"ocsp-metric-val\">40%</span><span class=\"ocsp-metric-lbl\">Reduction in billing errors after switching</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-footer\">\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag ocsp-tag-p\">Infrastructure</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-link\">Read case study <svg class=\"ocsp-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</div>\n</a>\n Card 2: SFC Infratech \n<a class=\"ocsp-card ocsp-anim ocsp-d1\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/sfc-infratech/\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-from\"><svg class=\"ocsp-from-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg><span class=\"ocsp-from-txt\">Switched from paper muster rolls</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-company\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-logo\" style=\"background:#d1fae5!important;\"><span class=\"ocsp-logo-init\" style=\"color:#059669!important;\">S</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-company-txt\"><div class=\"ocsp-name\">SFC Infratech</div><div class=\"ocsp-role\">Civil contractor, India</div></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-stars\"><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp-quote\">“We had ghost worker problems and daily disputes over attendance. After SiteFlow, every worker checks in with face recognition and payroll runs automatically. Not a single dispute since.”</p>\n<div class=\"ocsp-metric\"><span class=\"ocsp-metric-val ocsp-metric-val-g\">Zero</span><span class=\"ocsp-metric-lbl\">Payroll disputes since going live on SiteFlow</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-footer\">\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag ocsp-tag-g\">Civil Contractor</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-link\">Read case study <svg class=\"ocsp-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</div>\n</a>\n Card 3: Cyath Contracting \n<a class=\"ocsp-card ocsp-anim ocsp-d2\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/case-study-cyath-contracting/\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-from\"><svg class=\"ocsp-from-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"#b45309\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg><span class=\"ocsp-from-txt\">Switched from disconnected tools</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-company\">\n<div class=\"ocsp-logo\" style=\"background:#dbeafe!important;\"><span class=\"ocsp-logo-init\" style=\"color:#1d4ed8!important;\">C</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-company-txt\"><div class=\"ocsp-name\">Cyath Contracting</div><div class=\"ocsp-role\">Specialist contractor, UAE</div></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-stars\"><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span><span class=\"ocsp-star\">★</span></div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"ocsp-quote\">“Operating across Dubai projects, we needed one system for site and finance. SiteFlow handles everything — daily progress reports to vendor billing. Setup was faster than we expected.”</p>\n<div class=\"ocsp-metric\"><span class=\"ocsp-metric-val ocsp-metric-val-g\">4 days</span><span class=\"ocsp-metric-lbl\">To go fully live in Dubai</span></div>\n<div class=\"ocsp-footer\">\n<span class=\"ocsp-tag ocsp-tag-b\">Middle East</span>\n<span class=\"ocsp-link\">Read case study <svg class=\"ocsp-link-svg\" fill=\"none\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"></path></svg></span>\n</div>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n FAQ \n<div class=\"ocfq-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocfq-inner\">\n<div class=\"ocfq-head ocfq-anim\">\n<div class=\"ocfq-eyebrow\"><div class=\"ocfq-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"ocfq-ey-txt\">FAQ</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"ocfq-h2\">Questions about switching to SiteFlow</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-grid\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\">\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Is SiteFlow more affordable than other construction software?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes, for Indian and Gulf teams. Most global construction software charges per user in USD, which adds up quickly when your site workforce is large. SiteFlow is priced per project in INR, meaning you can add unlimited users — site engineers, supervisors, subcontractors — without costs scaling up. For teams based in India or the Middle East, SiteFlow is typically a fraction of the cost of international alternatives for the same team size.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim ocfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How long does it take to switch from another tool to SiteFlow?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Most teams are fully live within 3 to 5 days. SiteFlow includes free onboarding — a dedicated team walks your site engineers and office staff through the platform specific to your project type. There is no implementation partner needed, no months-long rollout, and no additional setup fees. You can also run SiteFlow in parallel with your current tool during the transition.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Does SiteFlow work for Middle East construction projects?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. SiteFlow has active clients running projects in the UAE, Qatar, and Saudi Arabia. The platform supports multi-currency billing, works across time zones, and handles Gulf-specific workflows including subcontractor RA billing and materials tracking. The case studies from Cyath Contracting in Dubai and M. Munif Al Otaibi Contracting in Saudi Arabia are both live Middle East deployments.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim ocfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Can I import data from my current software into SiteFlow?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes. SiteFlow supports data import for BOQ, material library, party master, rate library, and labour records from Excel. If you are migrating from another platform, the onboarding team will help you map and import your existing data. Historical project data can be carried over so your team does not start from scratch.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Does SiteFlow integrate with Tally or Zoho Books?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Yes, both. SiteFlow integrates directly with Tally and Zoho Books for accounting sync. This means your site expenses, vendor bills, and payroll data flow into your accounting software automatically — no double entry. Most alternatives in this space do not support Tally integration, which is the primary accounting software used by Indian construction companies.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim ocfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">Is there a free trial available?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">SiteFlow does not offer a self-serve trial because construction software works better when set up with your actual project data rather than dummy data. Instead, the process starts with a 10-minute live demo tailored to your project type, followed by a pilot on a real project with full onboarding support included. This gives you a much more accurate picture of whether SiteFlow fits your workflow.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">How do the comparisons on this page work?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">Each comparison is written specifically for Indian and Middle East construction teams. We evaluate software on criteria that actually matter in this market: BOQ support, GPS and face attendance, subcontractor billing, Tally and Zoho integration, INR pricing, and onboarding speed. We do not accept sponsored placements and do not inflate SiteFlow’s scores — if a competitor does something better we say so.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"ocfq-item ocfq-anim ocfq-d1\" data-open=\"false\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"ocfq-btn\" onclick=\"ocfqToggle(this)\"><span class=\"ocfq-btn-txt\" itemprop=\"name\">What happens after I book a demo?</span><span class=\"ocfq-arr\">+</span></button><div class=\"ocfq-body\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\"><p class=\"ocfq-ans\" itemprop=\"text\">The demo is a live 30-minute walkthrough of SiteFlow specific to your project type — no generic slides, no sales presentation. An onboarding manager shows you the exact workflows your team would use. If it is a fit, you start a pilot on one real project with full setup support. There is no long-term contract required and no pressure to commit immediately.</p></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n CTA \n<div class=\"ocfc-outer\">\n<div class=\"ocfc-inner ocfq-anim ocfq-d1\">\n<div class=\"ocfc-eyebrow\"><div class=\"ocfc-ey-dot\"></div><span class=\"ocfc-ey-txt\">Stop comparing. Start building.</span></div>\n<h2 class=\"ocfc-h2\">You have seen how SiteFlow compares.<br/><em class=\"ocfc-h2-em\">See how it runs your sites.</em></h2>\n<p class=\"ocfc-sub\">500 plus construction teams across India and the Middle East made the switch. A 30-minute demo shows you exactly how SiteFlow works for your project type — with your data, not dummy data.</p>\n<div class=\"ocfc-btns\">\n<a class=\"ocfc-btn-primary\" href=\"#ct-popup-48098\">Book a Free Demo</a>\n<a class=\"ocfc-btn-outline\" href=\"https://siteflow.com/customers/\">Read Case Studies</a>\n</div>\n<p class=\"ocfc-fine\">No credit card  ·  No long-term contract  ·  Free onboarding included</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n"
}